1.0.0.name: wordpress/paul-google-maps-coordinates
1.0.0.description:
This plugin is used to find latitude and longitude of an address that you specify. You can also drag the marker for more precision if the plugin result is not so good... Then you can use the coordinates to create a new google map, to set a new poi in your car navigator or many others things that you can think!

History:<br/> 1.0.2 Fixed bug IE7 and map types<br/> 1.0.1 Add intenationalization<br/> 1.0.0 First release
